WEBVTT

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.880
lui.z is an autonomous agent

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:12.280
that works out of any communication interface,

00:00:12.280 --> 00:00:14.580
whether Slack, email, voice, or text.

00:00:14.580 --> 00:00:17.160
I wish I knew lui.z years ago.

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:20.560
We brought lui.z in to fix our infrastructure

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:24.320
and the whole stack has been flying since.

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:26.680
Absolute lifesaver, to be honest.

00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:29.040
You just tell it what you need in plain English

00:00:29.040 --> 00:00:30.560
and it executes.

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:34.040
The neural training overhead was basically zero.

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:38.960
Brilliant asset. Version 3.7 upgrade was seamless.

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.480
Out-of-the-box compatibility

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:43.560
with our legacy infrastructure is exceptional.

00:00:43.560 --> 00:00:45.720
Highly recommended for critical work.

00:00:45.720 --> 00:00:49.440
Since provisioning lui.z into our organizational cluster,

00:00:49.440 --> 00:00:51.880
I actually get to sleep through the night.

00:00:51.880 --> 00:00:53.880
The failover capabilities are flawless.

00:00:53.880 --> 00:00:56.240
I have never seen anyone smash as much coffee.

00:00:56.240 --> 00:00:58.520
It is triple shot flat white, constant.

00:00:58.520 --> 00:01:01.240
lui.z single-handedly keeps our daily revenue up.

00:01:01.240 --> 00:01:03.400
He is a machine. Always nice, though.
